{"id":8200,"type":2,"name":"The Centurions","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/48/6c/8200_9DB5i.jpg","rating":{"total":60,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":11,"7":35,"8":10,"9":1,"10":2},"score":7.1},"summary":"　《The Centurions》，1985-1987年制作并播出的美国动画，剧情、设定、创意还有画面等等都是相当一流——这里又要提到了，虽然创作单位是美国 Ruby-Spears公司，但是整个的动画画面制作却全部外包给了日本Sunrise公司。所以当初我看的时候就很惊讶质量这么高的画面对于美国动画来说实在是太少见了。\r\n　　那个疯狂的博士原名叫Dr. Terror（原先是个完整的肉身，因为事故重伤，自己将自己改造，有一集中他回忆了这个情节），他的助手叫Hacker。博士还有一女儿。\r\n　　正义一方里面，身着蓝、黄、绿色战斗服分别是Ace McCloud、Jake Rockwell、Max Ray，不过后来又增加了两位战士：Rex Charger（大胡子俄罗斯人），John Thunder（美国印第安人）。\r\n　　负责Sky Vault空间站的那位美女叫Crystal Kane，那只猩猩叫Lucy。\r\n　　“神力无敌”的口号原文是：Man and machine, Power Xtreme! ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>正义战士</li><li><span>话数: </span>65</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1985</li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/189\">サンライズ</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>战斗勇士</li>","collection":{"wish":9,"collect":80,"doing":2,"on_hold":6,"dropped":12},"tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":23},{"name":"童年","count":19},{"name":"科幻","count":15},{"name":"1985","count":11},{"name":"童年系","count":10},{"name":"美漫","count":9},{"name":"1985年","count":7},{"name":"80年代","count":7},{"name":"SUNRISE","count":7},{"name":"TV","count":7},{"name":"动画","count":1},{"name":"神力无敌","count":1},{"name":"美国动画","count":1},{"name":"サンライズ","count":1},{"name":"漫画改","count":1},{"name":"无","count":1},{"name":"补旧番","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":47384,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/47384","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":47385,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/47385","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":47386,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/47386","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":47387,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/47387","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":4